      • get

        public static Relation get(int i)
        Gets a Relation from a difference: If i is 0, EQUAL is returned, if i is greater than 0, GREATER is returned, otherwise SMALLER.
        Parameters:
        i - an integer
        Returns:
        i == 0 ? Relation.EQUAL : i > 0 ? Relation.GREATER : Relation.SMALLER

      • get

        public static Relation get(double d)
        Gets a Relation from a difference: If d is 0, EQUAL is returned, if d is greater than 0, GREATER is returned, otherwise SMALLER. If d is Double.NaN, then NOT_EQUAL is returned
        Parameters:
        d - a double
        Returns:
        d == 0 ? Relation.EQUAL : d > 0 ? Relation.GREATER : Relation.SMALLER, or Relation.NOT_EQUAL if Double.isNan(d)

      • is

        public boolean is(Relation other)
        Test whether this relation is fulfilled if another is, i.e. if the parameter relation fulfils X rel Y, then this relation fulfils X rel Y as well.
        Parameters:
        other - another Relation
        Returns:
        Whether this relation is part of the given relation, e.g. GREATER_OR_EQUAL.is(EQUAL) returns true.
